additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Pocket crust (wheat flour, water, thickeners (1422, 464), milk solids, sugar, salt, emulsifiers (471, 435, 322 (soy)), vegetable oils (canola, palm, coconut), yeast, natural flavour), mozzarella and cheddar cheese (18%) (milk, salt, enzyme, starter cultures), sauce (water, tomato paste, thickeners (1442, 1412, 1422), herbs, vegetable powders, (wheat), spices), manufactured bacon (9%) (pork, water, potato starch, salt, soy protein isolate, pork protein, antioxidants (307b, 316), mineral salts (451, 450, 508), vegetable gum (407a), hydrolysed vegetable protein, fermented rice, preservative (250)).

description: A traditional round pizza crust filled with creamy mozzarella, cheddar cheese and bacon.
name: Frozen Cheese & Bacon Pizza Pockets
